				<td colspan="2"><span>I say it's still worth it, but certainly more and more possible to do without.
<br />

<br />
It's still good stats and a proc, and you don't have to worry about instruments every again <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
However-
<br />

<br />
Tear shaped ring = string mod
<br />
Battle-drummer main gauche = percussion mod
<br />
Trobadour mace = brass mod 
<br />

<br />
Mmc 220 Aug3 Gravestone of Dire Melodies
<br />
Lore, Type:WindInstruments(1.6)  Brd All 
<br />

<br />
And you can get Singing TRIBUTE mod.
<br />

<br />
So it's quite possible to fill in slots and get &quot;nearly epic'd&quot;, but I much prefer using my ONE slot and ONE weapon  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-11.gif" border="0" alt="Cool" hspace="2" />
